{"tid":1356682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"寫信讚揚利君雅","createTime":"2019-07-23T14:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:41:08.000Z","uid":12405,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9553ca282c5c33fedfd35b12e6abaee78bbe64ad","tid":1356682,"uid":12405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:27:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家都知道利君雅係問完林鄭之後應該都會受到唔少政治壓力，有啲未經fact check嘅post 更加話佢有機會會受罰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府寫appraisal 其中一樣睇嘅野就係public view，有見及此，我希望大家都可以幫幫手，有時間就寫一封信俾RTHK表揚一位咁有良心嘅記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我英文能力有限，都寫咗少少野俾大家參考，英文好嘅巴打絲打都可以幫我執執佢造福大家<br />\n<br />\n都提提大家記得要加或者改少少content，因為同一個內容嘅email 政府係只會當一個的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然，如果有時間大家都應該寫埋俾RTHK其他出色嘅 reporter 同 producer, 特別係視點31嘅同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5755f7a30acd87f59139df67e713a904d9614c6e","tid":1356682,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7811ae275a713b4f0fcc1b05d8c2dc7f855295a","tid":1356682,"uid":228083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:59:29.000Z","msg":"呢個要啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff95f1145203a35b0fee336a5206fe7abfac11d6","tid":1356682,"uid":262053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d861c51cbf9921cf3378f3ec0c14cb9b4763bc12","tid":1356682,"uid":188337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df4ef29adece7147fa4bb104b361e9c4f17cdfe1","tid":1356682,"uid":265857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09